\]

\end_inset

 To show that 
\begin_inset Formula $T^{*}=T^{-1},$
\end_inset

 we want to show that 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left\langle T^{-1}(x),y\right\rangle =\left\langle T^{*}(x),y\right\rangle =\left\langle x,T(y)\right\rangle 
\]

\end_inset

for all 
